TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi beforefieldinit ResolveNonMSBuildProjectOutput extends Microsoft.Build.Tasks.ResolveProjectBase

summary.span: Determina los archivos de salida de las referencias de proyecto que no son de MSBuild.

span.span: Determines the output files for non-MSBuild project references.

remarks.format: ## Remarks El `ResolveNonMSBuildProjectOutput` tareas busca una propiedad especial establecida por el [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] IDE para la lista de GUID de proyecto y sus resultados asociados.The `ResolveNonMSBuildProjectOutput` task searches for a special property set by the [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] IDE for the list of project GUIDs and their associated outputs. El IDE solo resuelve previamente no -[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] proyectos y de esta manera separa [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] referencias de no son del proyecto[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] referencias.The IDE only pre-resolves non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projects and in this way separates [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references from non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] references. El IDE devuelve la lista de [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] proyectos como UnresolvedProjectReferences.The IDE returns the list of [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projects as UnresolvedProjectReferences. Esto permite que la tarea más eficaz usar [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] mecanismos para manipular simplemente el [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] referencias del proyecto, como.This enables the task to use more powerful [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] mechanisms to manipulate just the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references, such as. llamar a destinos concretos de referencias para obtener el nombre de archivo de manifiesto, que no sería posible con una lista mixta de [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] y no-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] referencias del proyecto.calling into specific targets of references to get the manifest file name, which would not be possible with a mixed list of [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] and non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references.

remarks.format: ## Remarks Puesto que [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] solo resuelve previamente no -[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] proyectos, los elementos de referencia de proyecto que no se pudieron resolver mediante la lista de resultados previamente resuelta están en el [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] formato.Since [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] only pre-resolves non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projects, the project reference items that could not be resolved using the pre-resolved list of outputs are in the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] format.
